name: COHMAP chron 2
notes: No C-14 dates, 3 stratigraphic dates from Horseshoe-2. 11.4k for high Picea before second rise in Betula, 9.5k for beginning of Picea decline, 8.5k for Pinus decline. Age bounds for application of the model: top = 8500; bottom = 12000.
